---
layout: layouts/base.njk
templateClass: tmpl-home
---

<main class="home">
  <div class="intro-home">
    <h2>Hello!</h2>
    <p>I am Todd Libby, I am a Senior Front End Developer from South Portland, Maine and I love creating things on the web. This is my personal site where I write about technology, web, and other miscellaneous things. Have a look around and enjoy!</p>
  </div>

  <article class="about-intro">
    <div class="home-container">
      <div class="home-img"><img src="/img/headshot.png" alt="Headshot of Todd" class="lazyload"></div>
        <h3>I have an obsession with learning things on the web. I am currently re-sharpening my vanilla JavaScript skills, learning Vue and React, playing around with Gatsby, immersed in some User Experience courses. I just finished and became certified in a W3C Introduction to Accessibility course and I am very passionate about accessibility on the web as well as diversity and inclusion in tech.</h3>
    </div>
  </article>

  <div class="articles">
    <h3>Latest Articles</h3>
      <ul class="article-sections">
        <li class="article-wrapper">
          {%- for post in collections.darkpatterns | reverse -%}
          <a href="{{ post.url }}"><img src="/img/ccleaner.jpg" alt="CCleaner by Piriform asking a user to download Google Chrome. This is a dark pattern in UX" loading="lazy" data-src="/img/ccleaner.jpg" class="lazyload" />
            <h4>{{ post.data.title }}</h4></a>
          {%- endfor -%}
        </li>

        <li class="article-wrapper">
          {%- for post in collections.userdefendersbookclub | reverse -%}
            <a href="{{ post.url }}"><img src="/img/udbc.jpg" alt="User Defenders Book Club" loading="lazy" data-src="/img/udbc.jpg" class="lazyload" />
            <h4>{{ post.data.title }}</h4></a>
          {%- endfor -%}
        </li>

        <li class="article-wrapper">
          {%- for post in collections.colorcontrast | reverse -%}
          <a href="{{ post.url }}"><img src="/img/wcagcc.png" alt="An online color contrast checker" loading="lazy" data-src="/img/wcagcc.png" class="lazyload" />
            <h4>{{ post.data.title }}</h4></a>
          {%- endfor -%}
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </main>